 />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=1f005981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\nFb: shorturl.at/kqtJM<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstandbyeducatorshk%3Figshid%3Djuzv8s7rtxb5&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=e4fb8459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5</a>"},{"pid":"012b9ed9bdf883a675188251ce3903736715d393","tid":1775290,"uid":116265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"講過介意都唔理你，甚至嘈交都要同佢維繫關係。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都已經唔關佢係唔係同ex有冇嘢問題。<br />\n係佢根本唔care你<br />\n飛左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8362d7c9aa52849191556ef3edcdac7c7a8cebf0","tid":1775290,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"樓主咪免費飛機杯"},{"pid":"da4d51ba7245ef08f200c265d03aa2caab01796e","tid":1775290,"uid":323360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"335e6ed8b6e29d27f05ad840e7ea21a94f9c8249","tid":1775290,"uid":213499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a1041a4ee8964fdbcf4aa03d39c0cfae57f351a","tid":1775290,"uid":323360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34905d32e4dc4413c0f463df64dd971c54359d26","tid":1775290,"uid":213499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T19:27:34.000Z","msg":"冷靜嗰2個星期我無點理佢 <br />\n但佢不停氹返我 之後我就好心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"me心軟廢jj<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" cl